    "description": "HORAI Co., Ltd. engages in the insurance, real estate, dairy, and golf businesses in Japan. The company offers insurance agency services, including automobile, fire, and other non-life insurance, as well as life, and term and cancer insurance. It also engages in the rental, buying, selling, and brokerage of office buildings and residential properties, as well as leasing land to solar power generation companies. In addition, the company operates Senbonmatsu ranch; manufactures and sells milk and dairy products; and engages in breeding, milking, and feed production of dairy cattle. Further, it is involved in the management of restaurants, amusement facilities, and other industrial tourism facilities; and operation of Horai Country Club and Nishinasuno Country Club. The company was incorporated in 1928 and is headquartered in Chuo, Japan."
